com.fasterxml.clustermate.client.ahc

Class AHCGetCallResult<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fasterxml.clustermate.client.call.CallResult
      • com.fasterxml.clustermate.client.call.GetCallResult<T>
        • com.fasterxml.clustermate.client.ahc.AHCGetCallResult<T>

  • public final class AHCGetCallResult<T>
extends GetCallResult<T>
    Container for results of a single GET call to a server node. Note that at most one of '_fail' and '_result' can be non-null; however, it is possible for both to be null: this occurs in cases where communication to server(s) succeeds, but no content was found (either 404, or deleted content).
